# API Contracts

Base URL: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (default `http://localhost:8000/api`)

## Response shapes

- Success list: `{ data: T[], meta: { current_page, last_page, total }, links }`
- Success item: `{ data: T }` or resource wrapper from Laravel
- Error: `{ message: string, errors?: Record<string, string[]> }`

## Auth

- `POST /register`, `POST /login` — sets session cookie
- `GET /user` — current user (401 if guest)
- `POST /logout` — clears session
- All authenticated requests need `withCredentials: true` + CSRF cookie from `/sanctum/csrf-cookie`

## Pagination

`?page=1&per_page=12`

## Filters (cats)

`search`, `gender`, `breed`, `max_age_months`, `max_fee_cents`, `traits` (comma slugs), `sort` (newest|rating|fee-asc|fee-desc)

Update both sides when adding or renaming fields.
